TestNG Listeners
-----------------------
To create post actions after execution is done, we use Listener class.

Step 1. Create test case
Step 2. Create listener class (I Test Listner is an interface)
Step 3. Create xml file and include both test case & listener class

---------------------------------------
Methods of implementing listener class
---------------------------------------
Method 1
--------
class myListener implements ITestListener
{

}

--------
Method 2
--------
class myListener extends TestListenerAdapter
{

}

-------------
Extent report
-------------
Third party dependency, get from - https://extentreports.com/ OR mvnrepository - extentreports

ExtentSparkReporter - UI of the report
ExtentReports - populate common info on the report (OS name, browser name, model name)
ExtentTest - creating test cases in the report and update status of the test methods








